uyouts founded   years ago  headquarters  park avenue new york city new york us total assets  billion  website wwwangelogordoncom angelo gordon  company is an american alternative investment manager founded in november  by john m angelo and michael l gordon who together ran the arbitrage department of lf rothschild in the s the firm is  employeeowned secregistered and has nearly  employees and more than  investment professionals angelo gordon focuses on four main investment disciplines credit real estate private equity and multistrategy within those broad categories the firm offers products in distressed debt and noninvestment grade corporate credit convertible and merger arbitrage residential and consumer debt energy direct lending real estate private equity real estate debt and lending net lease real estate private equity multistrategy and middle market direct lending angelo gordon offers two types of investment structures openended hedge fund products and closedended private equitystyle products the firm is headquartered in new york city with additional offices worldwide including in san francisco los angeles chicago houston london amsterdam hong kong seoul frankfurt and tokyo contents  history  management committee  awards and recognition  investments  references  external links  additional references historyedit john angelo and michael gordon founded the firm on strategies with which they had  years prior experience distressed securities risk arbitrage and convertible arbitrage the multistrategy platform was added in  as a way to offer investors a single fund which captured many of angelo gordon’s investment strategies and which could tactically allocate as markets shifted in  the leveraged loan business was added as an extension of the distressed debt business the firm began buying real estate as early as  through investments in the distressed debt of bankrupt real estate companies in  as real estate markets buckled under the weight of too much debt the firm launched its opportunistic real estate strategy investments with the goal of improving and repositioning the property by increasing operating income in early  the company added core plus real estate to its real estate strategies as it was able to benefit from its operating partner network and purchase high quality real estate since  the firm has expanded its real estate offerings through a dedicated opportunistic asian real estate strategy in the wake of the global financial crisis of  and the european banking crisis of  angelo gordon added european real estate to its strategies as prices were depressed and liquidity was severely curtailed in the region net lease real estate strategy was established in  to focus on below investment grade tenants angelo gordon further expanded into the intersections of real estate and credit with the addition of real estate debt in  and residential and consumer debt in  in  angelo gordon was one of only nine private investment firms to partner with the us department of the treasury the board of governors of the federal reserve system and the federal deposit insurance corporation in ppip—the privatepublic investment partnership the us government invested alongside the selected firms to unlock the frozen credit markets in the wake of the global financial crisis this was a successful program the firm took advantage of the post financial crisis contraction in bank lending to smaller companies through senior secure direct lending to energy companies in  and to middle market borrowers in the private equity sponsor community in  in october  larry schloss became the president of angelo gordon and co in march  mr schloss left the firm cofounder john m angelo died in  management committeeedit mr michael l gordon cofounder ceo and chief investment officer cio mr kirk wickman chief operating officer  mr josh baumgarten deputy cio and coportfolio manager multistrategy mr adam schwartz head of us  europe real estate  awards and recognitionedit angelo gordon’s portfolio managers have in recent years been noted for top performance in their investment strategies angelo gordon’s cmbs fund and the noninvestment grade corporate credit fund were recognized by bloomberg for best performance for directional fixed income   the rmbsabs fund appeared in barron’s top  hedge funds in  and in  angelo gordon’s flagship multistrategy fund appeared in business insider’s  most successful hedge funds in  bloomberg ‘s  top performing large hedge funds in  and won the award for creditflux best credit multistrategy in  investmentsedit angelo gordon operates three basic types of investment vehicles illiquid strategies — include a variety of investment strategies distressed securities private equity triple net lease and real estate liquid strategies — credit opportunities convertible arbitrage and risk arbitrage multistrategy — takes advantage of attractive alternative investment opportunities from a range of the firms disciplines referencesedit  murray sean  july  deal alert angelo gordon acquires reliant funding debanked retrieved  september    company profile for angelo gordon  co lp bloomberg retrieved  june    a b c d profile ipe retrieved  january  permanent dead link  a b c d e f company overview of angelo gordon  co bloomberg businessweek retrieved  january    angelo gordon  co wallstreetoasiscom retrieved  january    fabrikant geraldine business people  officials at rothschild leaving to start firm new york times november    financial news hff retrieved  april    through the cycle senior secured loans poised to perform pdf angelo gordon  co retrieved  january    hu bei  february  angelo gordon seeks up to  billion for asia real estate fund retrieved  january    nycs angelo gordon aims at doubling european exposure to €bn property investor europe  march  archived from the original on  january  retrieved  january    angelo gordon  co announces closing of ag net lease realty fund lp with commitments of  million pr newswire  jan